# Vault SSOT for path rules

Path-specific engineering rules live in the vault, not in this file.

**Index:** `../whatorder-vault/Projects/WhatOrder/ai-rules/README.md`

When a scoped rule below activates, **read the matching vault file with the Read tool before editing** and follow it completely.

To change a rule, edit the vault `ai-rules/*.md` file and commit to `whatorder-vault`. Do not edit rule content in `.cursor/rules/*.mdc` wrappers.
